Employee Access

Thursday, October 17, 2013 11:54:00 AM


Employee Access
Welcome the CoreCivic employee internal application access page. Please click on one of the following links to access your CoreCivic internal applications.
Outlook Web Access
The CoreCivic Employee Portal
Citrix Applications
VPN Access
CoreCivic BOP Facility Citrix Access

This site is monitored and for use by CoreCivic employees only. Any unauthorized access will be reported and prosecuted to the full extent of the law.



