Day in the Life of a CCA Corrections Transportation Officer– 



Detention Officer Joel Oscarson is a transportation department officer at CCA's Nevada Southern Detention Center (NSDC) in Pahrump, Nevada. NSDC is owned and operated by CCA and supports the United States Marshals Service (USMS) as a detention facility for pretrial detainees being processed through the federal courts system in Las Vegas.







