A federal judge says he won't put a lawsuit against a major private prison company on hold while the FBI investigates the company for fraud







Prison company wants lawsuit held during FBI probe – 



Private prison company Corrections Corporation of America is asking a federal judge to put an Idaho lawsuit on hold while an FBI investigation into the company is underway







FBI investigates prison company – 



FBI has launched an investigation of the Corrections Corporation of America







Idaho lawmakers seek FBI inquiry into prison– 



Lawmakers concerned that Idaho State Police lacks both manpower and expertise needed to properly investigate Nashville, Tenn.-based company's activities in Idaho




